body: Ἐχῖνος, sea urchin, Echinus lividus; another species, with hard spines, is Cidaris hystrix, also a long species, Amphidetus Mediterraneus, _Forbes_, 10, 11; eatable kinds, 86; small species, E. saxatilis; white species at Torone, E. decadactylus, _ib._, 87, 94; at what season they are full of ova, 110.
